<article>

<h1 class="call"><a name="get-a-property">GET /properties/:id</a></h1>

<p>Returns extended information for a given <a href="/api/core/#public-resources">public</a> property identified from its ID.</p>

<h4>Resource URL</h4>
<div class="preview">
  <pre><code class="no-highlight">GET http://api.lelylan.com/properties/:id</code></pre>
</div>

<h4>Parameters</h4>

<table class="zebra-striped">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="parameter">
        <span>id</span>
        <span class="info">required</span>
      </td>
      <td>
        The ID of the desired property.
      </td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h4>Example Request</h4>

<ul class="nav nav-tabs">
  <li class="active"><a href="#get-a-property-curl" data-toggle="tab" class="curl">Curl</a></li>
  <li><a href="#get-a-property-node" data-toggle="tab" class="node">Node</a></li>
  <li><a href="#get-a-property-javascript" data-toggle="tab" class="javascript">Javascript</a></li>
  <li><a href="#get-a-property-ruby" data-toggle="tab" class="ruby">Ruby</a></li>
</ul>

<div class="tab-content">
  <div class="tab-pane active" id="get-a-property-curl">
    <div class="preview">
        <pre><code class="no-highlight">curl http://api.lelylan.com/properties/&lt;id&gt;</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-pane" id="get-a-property-node">
    <div class="preview">
      <pre><code class="javascript">var Lelylan = require('lelylan-node')();
Lelylan.Property.find('&lt;id&gt;', callback);</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-pane" id="get-a-property-javascript">
    <div class="preview">
        <pre><code># todo</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="tab-pane" id="get-a-property-ruby">
    <div class="preview">
        <pre><code class="ruby">lelylan = Lelylan::Client.new
property = lelylan.property('&lt;id&gt;')</code></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<h4>Example header response</h4>

  <div class="preview"><pre><code class="no-highlight">HTTP/1.1 200 OK</code></pre></div>

<h4 id="property-representation">Example body response</h4>

<div class="preview"><pre><code>{
  "uri": "http://api.lelylan.com/properties/5041e9e9230de31300000001",
  "id": "5041e9e9230de31300000001",
  "name":" Intensity",
  "suggested": {"0": "Min", "25": "Low", "50": "Half", "75": "High", "100": "Max"},
  "default": "0",
  "created_at": "2012-09-01T10:56:41Z",
  "updated_at": "2012-09-01T10:56:41Z"
}</code></pre></div>

<h4>Body response explained</h4>

<dl>
<dd><span>uri</span> - Property URI.</dd>
<dd><span>id</span> - Property ID.</dd>
<dd><span>name</span> - Property name.</dd>
<dt><span>suggested</span> - List of suggested values. <a href="/community/faq#suggested-values">Learn more about</a>.</dt>
<dd><span>default</span> - Default property value assigned when the device is created.</dd>
</dl>

</article>

