<h1 class="call"><a name="get-all-properties">GET /properties</a></h1>

<p>Returns a list of owned (and <a href="/api/core/#public-resources">public</a>) properties.</p>

<h4>Resource URL</h4>
<div class="preview">
<pre><code class="no-highlight"># created properties
GET http://api.lelylan.com/properties</code><code class="no-highlight"># all properties
GET http://api.lelylan.com/properties/public</code></pre>
</div>

<h4>Parameters</h4>

<table class="zebra-striped">
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td class="parameter">
        <span>name</span>
